@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cgrapq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(0.89)
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.31)) - 0.52)
    v2 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.03) - 0.50) + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.90) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.49)))
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
